Package dungeonadventure.properties

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Chargeable
    Interface for chargeable objects
    Eatable
    Interface for Eatable Items
    Holdable
    Marker interface for Items that the Player can hold in Inventory.
    Hostable
    Interface for Items that can take in other Items
    Inspectable
    Interface for inspectable Items, can be described and inspected
    Installable
    Marker interface for Items that are installable into other objects
    Nameable
    Interface for named objects.
    Openable
    Interface for Items that can be opened
    Playable
    Interface for objects with playback-capabilities
    Powerable
    Interface for powerable objects.
    Threadable
    Extending interface Runnable for threadable objects
    Timeable
    Interface for timeable objects, namely Bomb and WaterPipe.
